                            <li>Do not copy, download, forward, or store confidential material on personal devices or cloud accounts without written approval; promptly report any loss or suspected breach.</li>
                            <li>Return or securely delete confidential information when it is no longer needed or when engagement ends, except where retention is legally required.</li>
                            <li>Nothing here limits lawful reporting to regulators or responding to valid legal orders after notifying Legend’s legal contact when allowed.</li>
